{
  "stem": "19895.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So going to synagogue, if I went by myself, or going to-- on the streets to school, I often took it off just that I would not go through a neighborhood which I knew that people were out there to get us.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had often been attacked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when you earlier asked questions about the classmate of mine or classmates of mine, I recall one incident when we were-- after school-- going home together, this classmate of mine and myself.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I felt very safe always in his presence.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a fighter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He could, he could beat up everybody, even if it was a number of years older than him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His name is Amicham Reichman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He's alive.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He's in Israel.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was part of the Israeli military establishment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I talked to him last time, I was calling in his memory this incident when he was the one who fought with me, fighting off this attack.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were attacked by so-called Hitlerjugends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And Hitlerjugend, was in Hungary, an organization which was a German organization.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But many of the young boys in that organization were German backgrounds or Germans from Germany placed in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That organization was a very strong, major organization of Nazi teachings and background.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were like above everybody else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's the group we faced, the two of us at the time, when I recall this attack on the street.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We, we left that scene with bruises and bleeding nose, but so did they.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was just a major fight by 16 and 18-year-old children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The other group was older than us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were then called into the director's office of our Budapest Jewish high school, because the organization called on us that we have done some major attack on them.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
